text: Milan Corryn (born 4 April 1999) is a Belgian professional footballer who plays for AS Trenčín as a midfielder. ==Club career== ===AS Trenčín=== Corryn made his professional Fortuna Liga debut for AS Trenčín against Senica in September 15, 2018. Trenčín won the away game 2:0. He came on in the 77th minute replacing Joey Sleegers and was booked with a yellow card immediately after.
